          "Patient Name,Payer,CPT Code,ICD-10,Status,Missing Docs,Revenue At Risk,Submitted Date",
          "Smoke Patient,Aetna,72148,M54.5,p2p,\"imaging report, physician order\",1200,2026-02-10",
